Class MemorySelectable

Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseMemorySelectable
public class MemorySelectable
extends Object
implements Selectable

Implements a collection of Identifiable Data that is stored in memory. The iterator returned by the iterator method is guaranteed to be sorted by ObjectID.

Warning: This class is not synchronized, you need to provide your own synchronization outside of this class.
